strings.Value: "So, we're playing monster bait tonight, eh?"
"We're definitely getting ambushed someday, if we keep camping with our butts out like this."
"I appreciate your courage, Amiri, but I wouldn't like it if something nasty disturbed our rest."
"You yearn for death. Not many accept the inevitability of the end. I like this side of you."
"Perhaps tonight, for a change, someone else will come instead of monsters? Someone friendly, charming, and carrying a basket of cookies…"
"Ha! The fearless Amiri is scared we're not disguising the camp? Don't be afraid, if someone attacks us at night, just hide in your tent. — I'll handle it."
